5/5  rDev +11.6%look: 5 | smell: 5 | taste: 5 | feel: 5 |  overall: 5This is one of my favorite beers!!  It is a truly unique imperial stout.  I give it a 5 out of 5.  I learned with the 2014 version (where I was fortunate enough to get an entire case) to let it age as it has a bitter taste that disappears with age.  That said, I had the 2015 version draught at 600 degrees and it was quite awesome without the aging.  I picked up a couple of 2016 today, so I thought I would go ahead and drink one of the 2015 bottles.
