4.28/5  rDev -4.5%look: 4.5 | smell: 4 | taste: 4.25 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 4.5Color: almost black, just hints of brown as it pours from the bottle. Beautiful. Medium brown head, coarse lacing, decent persistence. Would rate higher if lacing were finer.
