4.33/5  rDev -3.3%look: 4.5 | smell: 4 | taste: 4.5 | feel: 4 |  overall: 4.52010 bottle. Up until tonight, I have had three other experiences with The Abyss. All three were 2009, so you can guess where I'm going ... every one of them had some degree of infection. None were undrinkable, they were just disappointing. So tonight was a time for redemption.
