cherries, dark cocoa, bourbon, toasted oak. Sweet Jesus, this is pure
gold.
Mouth is immensely thick and chewy, heavy with tiny, tiny bubbles
throughout. Perfect and dense.
I do believe I could drink this complex and rich brew fovever, if it
