4.53/5  rDev +1.1%look: 4.5 | smell: 4 | taste: 5 | feel: 5 |  overall: 4Huge thanks to RichBeer for this world class beer. Vintage 2008, 22 oz. bottle, poured into my Stone Imperial Russian Stout tulip.
