4.8/5  rDev +7.1%look: 5 | smell: 5 | taste: 5 | feel: 4 |  overall: 4.522 ounce bottle covered in black wax purchased from Holiday Wine Cellar for eleven dollars, 2007 vintage, drank tonight during Lost and while playing some video games, took me over two hours to get through the whole bottle, poured into my Dogfish Head snifter
